Cisco-IOS-XR-ip-bfd-oper API API Reference

API generated from Cisco-IOS-XR-ip-bfd-oper@2017-09-07.yang

API Endpoint
http://{Controller-IP}:{Controller-Port}/restconf/operational/network-topology:network-topology/topology/topology-netconf/node/{{router}}/yang-ext:mount/
URL '/' code: %2F
Schemes: http
Version: 1.0.0

Paths

BFD - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ip-bfd-oper:bfd/

Retrieve operation of resource: bfd

200 OK
bfd_schema

400 Bad Request

Internal Error
